data.videoquestion: Vexed - The Good Fight - Bled Black
data.videoanswer:
Video of the 80s-90s Seattle band, Vexed. Partial versions of their 
songs were recorded, The Good Fight and Bled Black are featured from a 
show at House of Leisure Seattle, WA 199*. In keeping with a certain 
element of cinema verite the experience of House of Leisure was 
explored.
